<div class="examples">
<h4>Example Request:</h4>
<h4><div class="inline"></div></h4>
<pre class="example code prettyprint"><code class="language-bash">curl 'https://&lt;canvas&gt;/api/sis/courses/&lt;course_id&gt;/disable_post_to_sis' \
     -X PUT \
     -H "Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;" \
     -H "Content-Length: 0"</code></pre>
<h4><div class="inline"></div></h4>
<pre class="example code prettyprint"><code class="language-bash">curl 'https://&lt;canvas&gt;/api/sis/courses/&lt;course_id&gt;/disable_post_to_sis' \
     -X PUT \
     -H "Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;" \
     -H "Content-Length: 0" \
     -d 'grading_period_id=1'</code></pre>
